.page-content
  .page-header
    %h1
      Registration
      %small
        %i.icon-double-angle-right
        Hinduism Revealed
  .row
    .col-xs-12
      %form.form-horizontal{role: 'form'}
        .form-group
          %label.col-sm-3.control-label.no-padding-right{for: 'form-field-1'} Name
          .col-sm-9
            %input#form-field-4.col-xs-2.margin-right-10{placeholder: 'First Name', type: 'text'}/
            %input#form-field-4.col-xs-2.margin-right-10{placeholder: 'Middle Name', type: 'text'}/
            %input#form-field-4.col-xs-2{placeholder: 'Surname', type: 'text'}/
        .space-4
        .form-group
          %label.col-sm-3.control-label.no-padding-right{for: 'form-field-1'} Date of Birth
          .col-sm-3
            .input-group
              %input#id-date-picker-1.form-control.date-picker{'data-date-format' => 'dd-mm-yyyy', type: 'text'}/
              %span.input-group-addon
                %i.icon-calendar.bigger-110
        .space-4
        .form-group
          %label.col-sm-3.control-label.no-padding-right{for: 'form-field-1'} Sex
          .col-sm-9
            .control-group
              .radio
                %label
                  %input.ace{name: 'form-field-radio', type: 'radio'}/
                  %span.lbl Male
                %label
                  %input.ace{name: 'form-field-radio', type: 'radio'}/
                  %span.lbl Female
        .space-4
        .form-group
          %label.col-sm-3.control-label.no-padding-right{for: 'form-field-1'} Marrital Status
          .col-sm-9
            .control-group
              .radio
                %label
                  %input.ace{name: 'form-field-radio', type: 'radio'}/
                  %span.lbl Married
                %label
                  %input.ace{name: 'form-field-radio', type: 'radio'}/
                  %span.lbl Unmarried
        .space-4
        .form-group
          %label.col-sm-3.control-label.no-padding-right{for: 'form-field-1'} Education
          .col-sm-9
            %input#form-field-1.col-xs-10.col-sm-5{placeholder: '', type: 'text'}/
        .space-4
        .form-group
          %label.col-sm-3.control-label.no-padding-right{for: 'form-field-1'} Occupation
          .col-sm-9
            %input#form-field-1.col-xs-10.col-sm-5{placeholder: '', type: 'text'}/
        .space-4
        .form-group
          %label.col-sm-3.control-label.no-padding-right{for: 'form-input-readonly'}
            Residential Address
          .col-sm-9
            %textarea.col-xs-10.col-sm-5
        .space-4
        .form-group
          %label.col-sm-3.control-label.no-padding-right{for: 'form-field-1'} Mobile
          .col-sm-9
            %input#form-field-1.col-xs-10.col-sm-5{placeholder: '', type: 'text'}/
        .space-4
        .form-group
          %label.col-sm-3.control-label.no-padding-right{for: 'form-field-1'} Telephone
          .col-sm-9
            %input#form-field-1.col-xs-10.col-sm-5{placeholder: '', type: 'text'}/
        .space-4
        .form-group
          %label.col-sm-3.control-label.no-padding-right{for: 'form-field-1'} Email
          .col-sm-9
            %input#form-field-1.col-xs-10.col-sm-5{placeholder: '', type: 'text'}/
        .space-4
        .form-group
          %label.col-sm-3.control-label.no-padding-right{for: 'form-field-1'} Payment By
          .col-sm-9
            %select#form-field-select-1
              %option{value: 'AL'} Cash
              %option{value: 'AK'} Cheque
              %option{value: 'AZ'} DD
              %option{value: 'AR'} Net Banking
        .form-group
          %label.col-sm-3.control-label.no-padding-right{for: 'form-field-1'} Basic Pranic Healing
          .col-sm-9
            %input#form-field-4.col-xs-2.margin-right-10{placeholder: 'Place', type: 'text'}/
            %input#form-field-4.col-xs-2.margin-right-10{placeholder: 'Date OR Year', type: 'text'}/
            %input#form-field-4.col-xs-2{placeholder: 'Instructor', type: 'text'}/
        .hr.hr-24
        -#%h4.header.green Details of Pranic Healing Courses you have taken (as applicable)
        %div{style: 'text-align:justify'}
          .col-xs-12
            %p
              I, hereby state that, having had the privilege of being accepted as a student in GRAND MASTER CHOA KOK
              SUIâ€™S above-named course, do solemnly swear to keep Secret and Confidential, all the sacred teachings taught
              therein.
            %p
              On my Honour, I sincerely promise to preserve these sacred teachings in their purest form, and practice them in the
              proper and correct manner, guided by the golden rules and the Five Arhatic Virtues taught by Grand Master Choa
              Kok Sui. I also promise to prevent misuse or incorrect practice of these teachings by persons who have not been
              adequately instructed.
            %p
              With the Lord God as my witness, and my Higher Self as my guide, I shall uphold this Vow of Secrecy and I will
              not divulge to anybody, under any circumstances, verbally or through the reproduction of written material, or
              through some other form, in whole or in part, any of the teachings, principles and techniques from the course.
            %p
              I make this solemn vow freely and voluntarily, with no mental reservation or purpose of evasion.

            .checkbox
              %label
                %input{name: 'case[accepted]', type: 'hidden', value: 'no'}/
                %input#case_accepted{name: 'case[accepted]', type: 'checkbox', value: 'yes'}/
                I accept VOW OF SECRECY
            .space-10
        .clearfix
          .col-md-offset-3.col-md-9
            %input.btn.btn-info{name: 'commit', type: 'submit', value: 'Register'}/
            %input.btn{name: 'commit', type: 'reset', value: 'Reset'}/